{"tid":245973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"終極防禦電腦病毒","createTime":"2017-05-16T15:52:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T15:56:53.000Z","uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bee8b83e1c002100cdfccc8c3803c9360371a24e","tid":245973,"uid":39853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:52:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">勒索病毒入侵XP電腦尷尬了！</span><br />\n配置太低被強制停止<br />\n上周爆發的勒索病毒至今已經讓數十萬PC受害，為了防止更多用戶感染，微軟和各家安全公司都紛紛給出更新補丁或者臨時防範策略。<br />\n不過，抵御勒索病毒的終極措施或許只是一台「古董PC」這麼簡單。台灣網友萊恩15日曬圖稱「電腦爛到病毒跑不動。」(WinXP+古董配置)<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/234821_e77170156bc5ca3eecc51104ceff897b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F234821_e77170156bc5ca3eecc51104ceff897b.jpg&h=4fe366fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來，萊恩的電腦最初也被勒索病毒感染，但就當病毒程序運行時卻被系統提示「失去響應」而強制終止。疑似配置太低無法滿足運行需求&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n面對這種尷尬局面，網友們也紛紛發表看法：「連病毒都嫌棄XP了」、「原來戰勝病毒的終極方法是用爛電腦」、「連中毒的資格都失去了。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/16/234836_0a43ff18e95672de4c77579289a178d9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F16%2F234836_0a43ff18e95672de4c77579289a178d9.jpg&h=cbbe3e6d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n來源：<a href=\"http://c.b0yp.com/h.6MS6aW?cv=5VsOZuQEMJE&amp;sm=22e5c9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fc.b0yp.com%2Fh.6MS6aW%3Fcv%3D5VsOZuQEMJE%26sm%3D22e5c9&d=bXICEjaVmsGxuRkiXhyD2LIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=57888bb8\" target=\"_blank\">http://c.b0yp.com/h.6MS6aW?cv=5VsOZuQEMJE&amp;sm=22e5c9</a>"},{"pid":"bbf52fada78148cc44a622fbf6b9de9cf1feea4d","tid":245973,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:56:53.000Z","msg":"中毒 即刻熄機，拆晒d ram, 插一條256mb 完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}